{
  "key": "SM-1103",
  "fields": {
    "summary": "Project Tracker - Cascade Template Management Screen",
    "description": {
      "type": "doc",
      "version": 1,
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "📝 User Story: Project Cascade Template Management Screen"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "As A: User using the Project Tracker  "
            },
            {
              "type": "hardBreak"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "I Want To: Access a management screen to create and configure project cascade templates, where each template contains multiple records with an associated number of days  "
            },
            {
              "type": "hardBreak"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "So That: I can efficiently set up and manage standardized project workflows with specific timing for each step."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Acceptance Criteria (ACs)"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "bulletList",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "listItem",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "AC1: The system provides a dedicated management screen for project cascade templates."
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "listItem",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "AC2: Users can create a new project cascade template and assign a name to it."
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "listItem",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "AC3: Each template allows users to add multiple records/steps, each with a configurable number of days."
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "listItem",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "AC4: Users can view, edit, and delete existing templates and their records."
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "listItem",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "AC5: The interface supports managing multiple project cascade templates."
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Scenario Example"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "bulletList",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "listItem",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "Input: User navigates to the cascade template management screen, creates a template named \"Site Launch,\" adds three steps (\"Design\" - 5 days, \"Procurement\" - 10 days, \"Installation\" - 7 days)."
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "listItem",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "Output: \"Site Launch\" template is saved with three steps, each displaying the correct number of days. User can edit or remove steps as needed."
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Original Description:"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "create a project cascade template management screen that lets them set up records with a number of days associated to each. Each project cascade template will have multiple values. and then there are multiple project cascade templates"
            },
            {
              "type": "hardBreak"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "*Note: Request came from Carlos in our on call meeting 4/1/26."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
